criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Aged 15 to 19 years;

          2. Perinatally HIV-infected;

          3. Receiving ART for at least 6 months;

          4. Fully aware of their HIV status

        Exclusion Criteria:

        1. Inability to read and/or speak English or Zulu or severe mental or physical illness
        preventing informed consent
